WEBVTT

00:02:28.156 --> 00:02:30.333
and I was able to step up immediately.

00:02:31.439 --> 00:02:32.823
Within five minutes,

00:02:32.847 --> 00:02:35.004
no staircase was safe from my advances.

00:02:35.028 --> 00:02:36.615
(Laughter)

00:02:36.639 --> 00:02:40.203
That very day, I climbed
a staircase of three flights,

00:02:40.227 --> 00:02:42.236
which I was quite impressed with as well,

00:02:42.260 --> 00:02:45.379
except I realized that I didn't know
how to get back down again.

00:02:45.403 --> 00:02:47.345
(Laughter)

00:02:47.702 --> 00:02:48.889
That was a long weekend.

00:02:48.913 --> 00:02:53.567
(Laughter)

00:02:53.591 --> 00:02:56.530
Now, in my past life
as an able-bodied person,

00:02:56.554 --> 00:02:58.082
I'd been a guitarist.

00:02:59.285 --> 00:03:00.595
I was alright as a player,